(3, '4eabe3eeb3d3ecd9f9', 1, '', '<p><br></p><p>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;&gt;&lt;!-- Include Editor style. --&gt;&lt;link href=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/froala-editor@3.1.0/css/froala_editor.pkgd.min.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; type=&quot;text/css&quot; /&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;sample&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Video upload example.&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;form&gt;&lt;textarea id=&quot;edit&quot; name=&quot;content&quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/form&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- Include Editor JS files. --&gt;&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/froala-editor@3.1.01/js/froala_editor.pkgd.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;!-- Initialize the editor. --&gt;&lt;script&gt;new FroalaEditor(&#39;#edit&#39;, {// Set the video upload URL.videoUploadURL: &#39;/upload_video.php&#39;,videoUploadParams: {id: &#39;my_editor&#39;},})&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</p><div data-element_type=\"widget\" data-id=\"4e10cd6\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\" id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 846.5px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-align: left; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-family: Nunito, Nunito; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-primary-font-family ), Nunito; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 2.6em; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-primary-font-weight ); line-height: 1; padding-top: 20px !important; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">Image Concepts</h2></div></div><div data-element_type=\"widget\" data-id=\"2fa8783\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 846.5px; margin-bottom: 18px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-family: Nunito, Nunito; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 40px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-family: Nunito, Nunito; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 1.566em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; padding-left: 10px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(0, 152, 247);\">Upload Image</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">For testing purposes, the Froala Rich Text Editor by default stores the images temporarily as a Blob file in the browser memory. While integrating the editor, you should upload them to your own server for privacy reasons, permanent storage and full control over them.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">This means that you have to handle the image upload and storage using a server-side language yourself. This article is meant to help you understand how the editor&#39;s image upload works.</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Nunito, Nunito; color: rgb(81, 81, 81); font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Upload Flow</em></h3><ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Include the image plugin file.</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Image is a plugin for the editor and the&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'>image.min.js</code> file must be included before being able to use it.</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Set the editor&#39;s image upload options.</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">When uploading images, you can customize up to 6 parameters and 5 events:<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/options#imageUploadParam\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"imageUploadParam\">imageUploadParam</a></code> is the name of the parameter that contains the image file information in the upload request. The default value is &quot;file&quot; but you can change it to whatever name you want.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/options#imageUploadURL\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"imageUploadURL\">imageUploadURL</a></code> is the URL where the upload request is being made.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/options#imageUploadParams\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"imageUploadParams\">imageUploadParams</a></code> are additional params that are passed in the upload request to the server.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/options#imageUploadMethod\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"imageUploadMethod\">imageUploadMethod</a></code> is the HTTP request type.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/options#imageMaxSize\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"imageMaxSize\">imageMaxSize</a></code> is the maximum image size that can be uploaded.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/options#imageAllowedTypes\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"imageAllowedTypes\">imageAllowedTypes</a></code> is an array with the image types allowed to be uploaded.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events#image.beforeUpload\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"image.beforeUpload\">image.beforeUpload</a></code> event is triggered before starting the upload request and it can be used to change the upload params or cancel the action.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events#image.uploaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"image.uploaded\">image.uploaded</a></code> event is triggered after a successfully image upload request, but before inserting the image in the editor.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events#image.inserted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"image.inserted\">image.inserted</a></code> event is triggered after inserting the image into the editor.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events#image.replaced\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"image.replaced\">image.replaced</a></code> event is triggered after replacing the image into the editor.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&bull;&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'><a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/events#image.error\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"image.error\">image.error</a></code> event is triggered if any errors occur during the upload process.</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">AJAX request from editor to the imageUploadURL link.</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">When an image is inserted into the WYSIWYG HTML editor, a HTTP request is automatically done to the server.</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The server processes the HTTP request.</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The server has to process the upload request, save the image and return a JSON containing a link to the uploaded image. The returned JSON needs to look like:&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'>{ &quot;link&quot;: &quot;path/to/image.jpg&quot; }</code></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">If you need help with the server side image upload process please check out the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/sdks/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 152, 247); transition: color 0.2s ease 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease 0s; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; box-shadow: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Froala SDKs</a>.</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The editor loads the image in browser.</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">When the request finishes, the editor will load the image. If the returned hashmap does not follow the right structure or the image cannot be loaded,&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"Lucida Console\", Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.85em; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); word-break: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\'>image.error</code> event is triggered.</p></li></ol><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The following snippet highlights how to initialize the Froala WYSIWYG HTML editor in order to upload images.</p><button style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 5px; margin: 4px 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; text-transform: none; appearance: button; position: absolute; right: 6px; border: 0px; cursor: pointer; padding: 5px; background: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Copy</button><pre style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", \"Courier New\", monospace; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: auto; display: block; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding: 2.5em 0.5em 0.5em !important; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 128); font-weight: normal;\">&lt;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 128); font-weight: normal;\">script</span>&gt;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">new</span> FroalaEditor(<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;.selector&#39;</span>, {\n    <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Set the image upload parameter.</span>\n    imageUploadParam: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;image_param&#39;</span>,\n\n    <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Set the image upload URL.</span>\n    imageUploadURL: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;/upload_image&#39;</span>,\n\n    <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Additional upload params.</span>\n    imageUploadParams: {<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">id</span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;my_editor&#39;</span>},\n\n    <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Set request type.</span>\n    imageUploadMethod: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;POST&#39;</span>,\n\n    <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Set max image size to 5MB.</span>\n    imageMaxSize: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\">5</span> * <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\">1024</span> * <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\">1024</span>,\n\n    <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Allow to upload PNG and JPG.</span>\n    imageAllowedTypes: [<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;jpeg&#39;</span>, <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;jpg&#39;</span>, <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;png&#39;</span>],\n\n    <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">events</span>: {\n      <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;image.beforeUpload&#39;</span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">function</span> (<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">images</span>) </span>{\n        <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Return false if you want to stop the image upload.</span>\n      },\n      <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;image.uploaded&#39;</span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">function</span> (<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">response</span>) </span>{\n        <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Image was uploaded to the server.</span>\n      },\n      <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;image.inserted&#39;</span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">function</span> (<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">$img, response</span>) </span>{\n        <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Image was inserted in the editor.</span>\n      },\n      <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;image.replaced&#39;</span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">function</span> (<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">$img, response</span>) </span>{\n        <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Image was replaced in the editor.</span>\n      },\n      <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(221, 17, 68);\">&#39;image.error&#39;</span>: <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">function</span> (<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">error, response</span>) </span>{\n        <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136); font-style: italic;\">// Bad link.</span>\n        <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">if</span> (error.code == <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 